'''磷酸氫二銨'''，或稱'''磷酸氫銨'''、'''磷酸一氫銨'''，是一種白色的晶體，水溶液呈中性。分子式為(NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>HPO<sub>4</sub>，可溶於[[水|水]]，加熱至155℃分解。

磷酸一氢铵会逐漸的分解釋放出[[氨氣|氨氣]]，而形成[[磷酸二氢铵|磷酸二氢铵]]。<ref>{{cite book |title=Phosphorus And Its Compounds - Volume I: Chemistry |page=503 |author=John R Van Wazer |year=1958 |publisher=Interscience Publishers, Inc |place=New York}}</ref>

:{{chem2|(NH4)2HPO4(s) <-> NH3(g) + (NH4)H2PO4(s)}}

==用处==
磷酸一氢铵可用作[[肥料|肥料]]。<ref name=IPNI2014>{{cite web
| last1 =IPNI
| title =Diammonium Phosphate
| url =http://www.ipni.net/publication/nss.nsf/0/66D92CC07C016FA7852579AF00766CBD/$FILE/NSS-17%20Diammonium%20Phosphate.pdf
| website =www.ipni.net
| publisher =International Plant Nutrition Institute
| access-date =21 July 2014
| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150924035955/http://www.ipni.net/publication/nss.nsf/0/66D92CC07C016FA7852579AF00766CBD/$FILE/NSS-17%20Diammonium%20Phosphate.pdf
| archive-date =24 September 2015
| url-status =live
}}</ref>当用作植物的肥料时，它会暂时增加[[土壤|土壤]]的[[pH|pH]]，但经过长时间的硝化处理后，用磷酸一氢铵处理过的土壤会变得比以前更具[[酸性|酸性]]。由于[[铵|铵]]在高碱性环境下会被转换成[[氨|氨]]，所以磷酸一氢铵和[[碱|碱]]不相容。磷酸一氢铵溶液的平均pH是7.5–8。<ref name='IPNI - DAP'>{{cite web |url= http://www.ipni.net/publication/nss.nsf/0/66D92CC07C016FA7852579AF00766CBD/$FILE/NSS-17%20Diammonium%20Phosphate.pdf |title= Nutrient Source Specifics: Diammonium Phosphate |access-date= 2012-12-10 |author= International Plant Nutrition Institute |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20121021041202/http://www.ipni.net/publication/nss.nsf/0/66D92CC07C016FA7852579AF00766CBD/$FILE/NSS-17%20Diammonium%20Phosphate.pdf |archive-date= 2012-10-21 |url-status= live }}</ref>

磷酸一氢铵也可以用作[[阻燃剂|阻燃剂]]。它降低了材料的燃烧温度，降低了最大重量损失率，并增加残留物。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=George |first1=C.W. |last2=Susott |first2=R.A. |title=Effects of Ammonium Phosphate and Sulfate on the Pyrolysis and Combustion of Cellulose |publisher=USDA Forest Service |journal=Research Paper INT-90 |place=Intermountain Forest and Range Experiment Station |date=April 1971 |url=https://openlibrary.org/b/OL16022833M/Effects_of_ammonium_phosphate_and_sulfate_on_the_pyrolysis_and_combustion_of_cellulose}}</ref>这些性质可用于扑灭野火，因为降低[[热裂解|热裂解]]温度和增加形成的焦炭量会减少可用燃料的量，并可能形成[[防火道|防火道]]。它是一些流行的商业消防产品的最大成分，也是“阻燃”卷烟的成分。<ref name="phoscheck">[http://phos-chek.com/uploads/File/pdfs/retardant/Phos-Chek%20259F,%20259R,%20259W%20MSDS.pdf Phos-Chek MSDS]{{dead link|date=September 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}, Phos-Chek website</ref>

磷酸一氢铵也可用于{{le|酵母可同化的氮|yeast assimilable nitrogen|酿酒}}和酿[[蜂蜜酒|蜂蜜酒]]中的酵母营养素，某些品牌卷烟的添加剂（据称是[[尼古丁|尼古丁]] 强剂），防止火柴余辉，[[糖|糖]]的纯化，焊接锡、铜、锌和黄铜的[[助焊剂|助焊剂]]，以及控制[[羊毛|羊毛]]上可溶于碱但不溶于酸的胶体染料[[沉淀|沉淀]]。<ref name="hand"/>

==天然存在==
磷酸一氢铵在天然中以罕见矿物phosphammite存在。<ref name="auto2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.mindat.org/min-3197.html|title=Phosphammite|website=www.mindat.org|access-date=8 November 2020|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107055708/https://www.mindat.org/min-3197.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ima-mineralogy.org/Minlist.htm|title=List of Minerals|date=21 March 2011|website=www.ima-mineralogy.org|access-date=8 November 2020|archive-date=2021-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211220223545/https://www.ima-mineralogy.org/Minlist.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>相关的磷酸二氢铵则以矿物biphosphammite的形式存在。<ref name="auto1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.mindat.org/min-678.html|title=Biphosphammite|website=www.mindat.org|access-date=8 November 2020|archive-date=2022-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107055712/https://www.mindat.org/min-678.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="auto"/>它们都与鸟粪沉积物有关。<ref name="auto2"/><ref name="auto1"/>

